Used along with FREE bit to determine the emulation suspend mode. Conventionally, when FREE bit is cleared, SOFT bit selects the mode. GPIO has FREE = 1, so SOFT bit does not affect functionality
For GPIO, the FREE bit is fixed at 1, which means GPIO runs free in emulation suspend mode
